<div class="de-u-flex de-u-flexAlignItemsCenter de-u-flexJustifyBetween">
  <div>
    <strong>Size: </strong>
    <span class="de-u-textDarkGray de-u-textMedium">
      Select a size
    </span>
  </div>
  <a
    href="#size-and-fit"
    data-drawer-id="size-guide-drawer"
    data-drawer-toggle-aria-label="Open the size guide dialog."
    data-drawer-action="open"
    class="de-u-flex de-u-flexAlignItemsCenter de-u-textBlue de-u-textSizeBase de-u-textMedium js-de-Drawer-toggle"
  >
    {% include 'product-icon--ruler' %}
    Size Guide
  </a>
</div>

{% comment %}
  Size Swatches
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %}
  The `SwatchObjects--size` modifier is intended to pair well with any
  combination of the following style variants:
  → `de-is-active`
  → `de-is-outofstock`
  → `de-is-soldout`
{% endcomment %}

